<h3 id="200">1.1. Creating new sales prices</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Sales prices are created and managed centrally in plentymarkets.
You can either create new sales prices with the help of an <em>assistant</em> or you can manually create new sales prices in the <em>setup menu</em>.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Either way, you’ll customise the sales prices to meet your needs.
You’ll give the sales prices names and you’ll decide which currencies, customer classes, marketplaces or other conditions should apply.</p>
</div>
