<p class="tableblock"><strong><em>Note</em></strong>: If you choose eBay or Amazon, then an additional configuration step will appear. During this step, you’ll tell plentymarkets which eBay or Amazon account the sales price should apply to.
Therefore, <a href="/en/markets/ebay/ebay-setup">link your eBay or Amazon account to plentymarkets</a> in advance.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Countries of delivery</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Should the sales price only apply to specific countries of delivery?
