</div>
<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="1300">2.1.2. Formula</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>How should the price be calculated?
For example, you could start with the purchase price and then add transportation costs, storage costs and taxes.
Finally, you could add a 7% profit margin on top.
In this case, the formula might look something like this:<br>
<code>(Purchase + Transport + Storage + VAT) * 1.07</code></p>
</div>
<div class="imageblock">
<div class="content">
<img src="{{plugin_path('PlentyManual')}}/images/item/settings/assets/formula.gif" alt="formula">
</div>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Writing the formula:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Enter a name for the formula if needed, e.g. base formula.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the entry field.<br>
→ A calculator opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Enter the formula:</p>
<div class="olist loweralpha">
<ol class="loweralpha" type="a">
<li>
<p>Enter numbers and mathematical symbols with the calculator or the keyboard.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Search for available variables and add them to your calculation (<span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-plus  "></i></span>).</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Apply</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
<h5 id="1350" class="discrete">Available variables</h5>
<div class="openblock collapseBox">
<div class="title"><strong>Variation</strong></div>
<div class="content">
<table class="tableblock frame-all grid-all stretch">
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 20%;">
