<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Purchase price</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Corresponds to the net purchase price under:<br>
<a href="/en/item/managing-items#280">Tab: Settings » Area: Costs » Option: Net purchase price</a></p>
